        "text_rAc6pc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sourced from dense native forests of Nepal’s “Golden Triangle,” Himalayan Cliff Honey is a delicious, creamy treat crafted by fuzzy honey bees bustling around the Mānuka tea tree. Himalayan Cliff Honey, like many honeys, is a highly prized ingredient that has been used for centuries in traditional medicine and is now gaining popularity as an integral part of maintaining a healthy lifestyle.</p><p>Sourced from dense native forests of Nepal’s “Golden Triangle,” Himalayan Cliff Honey is a delicious, creamy treat crafted by fuzzy honey bees bustling around the Mānuka tea tree. Himalayan Cliff Honey, like many honeys, is a highly prized ingredient that has been used for centuries in traditional medicine and is now gaining popularity as an integral part of maintaining a healthy lifestyle.</p><p>Sourced from dense native forests of Nepal’s “Golden Triangle,” Himalayan Cliff Honey is a delicious, creamy treat crafted by fuzzy honey bees bustling around the Mānuka tea tree. Himalayan Cliff Honey, like many honeys, is a highly prized ingredient that has been used for centuries in traditional medicine and is now gaining popularity as an integral part of maintaining a healthy lifestyle.<br/><br/><br/><br/></p>"
          }
